Titolo: Avernum: Escape from the Pit

Anno: 2011

Descrizione: Avernum: Escape from the Pit is a single-player role-playing video game developed by Spiderweb Software. It is the first game in the remade Avernum First Trilogy and the second ground-up rewrite of Exile: Escape from the Pit, released in 1995 (the first rewrite was Avernum, released in 2000). The game was re-released as a graphics and game engine update, as well as addressing Avernum 1-3 incompatibilities with newer versions of Mac OS X 10.7 Lion and newer.
The game was released for Mac OS X on December 14, 2011 A release date of April 2012 has been announced for Microsoft Windows and the iPad. and later for Valve's Steam on April 11, 2012.



Genere: Role-playing video game

Valutazione: 78
